    "name": "Ed & Edda: GRAND PRIX – Racing Champions",
    "steam_appid": 3288920,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Ed &amp; Edda: GRAND PRIX - Racing Champions</i> is a fast-paced racing game for the whole family. Parallel to the worldwide cinema release of GRAND PRIX OF EUROPE, the popular Europa-Park mascots Ed &amp; Edda are celebrating their video game debut! Climb into the cockpit with the two heroes of the film GRAND PRIX OF EUROPE and six other colourful characters. Fans of the film and the Europa-Park are looking forward to a reunion! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The races will take you to well-known locations across Europe.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288920/extras/5c7500cf54c5af5ce85b0c03073225d8.poster.avif?t=1758530003\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288920/extras/5c7500cf54c5af5ce85b0c03073225d8.webm?t=1758530003\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288920/extras/5c7500cf54c5af5ce85b0c03073225d8.mp4?t=1758530003\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether it's a <strong>Free Race</strong>, <strong>Point Chase, Time Trial</strong> or the <strong>Grand Prix</strong> - there are plenty of opportunities to put your driving skills to the test! And you'll need skill, because <i>Ed &amp; Edda: GRAND PRIX - Racing Champions</i> is really fast thanks to different boost techniques!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each character not only has their own vehicle, but also individual strengths and weaknesses. So every race feels different - depending on who you send onto the track.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288920/extras/14360d65dcf04c2886d482f35eb69fe4.poster.avif?t=1758530003\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288920/extras/14360d65dcf04c2886d482f35eb69fe4.webm?t=1758530003\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288920/extras/14360d65dcf04c2886d482f35eb69fe4.mp4?t=1758530003\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But <i>Ed &amp; Edda: GRAND PRIX - Racing Champions</i> isn't just fun to play alone: in <strong>local multiplayer</strong> for up to four people, you can experience exciting races together and create unforgettable moments - because Ed &amp; Edda is all about sharing the fun!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288920/extras/e856746e0798f06386a97af520551a1c.poster.avif?t=1758530003\" width=600 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288920/extras/e856746e0798f06386a97af520551a1c.webm?t=1758530003\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3288920/extras/e856746e0798f06386a97af520551a1c.mp4?t=1758530003\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Key features of <i>Ed &amp; Edda: GRAND PRIX - Racing Champions</i>:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fast-paced races: On fast tracks, around famous attractions from all over Europe, provide variety!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fast on the road: Various boost techniques ensure very high speed!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Eight playable characters: including Ed &amp; Edda, the famous Europa-Park mascots!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Many possibilities: Unique racers, clever power-ups and customisable vehicles ensure variety and fun! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiplayer: Up to four drivers can race at the same time - perfect for families and friends!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语<strong>*</strong>, 法语<strong>*</strong>, 德语<strong>*</strong><br><strong>*</strong>具有完全音频支持的语言",
